        <updateDate>2009-09-15T19:45:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Promoting Mortgage Responsibility Act - Amends the Truth in Lending Act to prohibit prepayment fees or penalties under any consumer credit transaction secured by the consumer's owner-occupied principal dwelling. </p> <p>Makes any prepayment penalty in violation of this prohibition unenforceable.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
